Samba/GPFS cluster

PREREQUISITES

* GPFS packages located in files/
* Credentials for enterprisesamba.com saved in files/sernet_creds
* Centos 6.6 base image puppet/centos-6.6 with Puppet installed

CONFIGURATION

* adjust variables in Vagrantfile
* adjust variables in manifest/cluster.pp
* adjust credentials in files/sernet_creds

GPFS RPMs:

  files/gpfs.base-3.5.0-0.x86_64.rpm
  files/gpfs.base-3.5.0-15.x86_64.update.rpm
  files/gpfs.docs-3.5.0-15.noarch.rpm
  files/gpfs.gpl-3.5.0-15.noarch.rpm
  files/gpfs.msg.en_US-3.5.0-15.noarch.rpm
